      "text": "みんな、今日は本当に\n会いに来てくれて、ありがとうございます……っ！",
      "startTime": 3.8710936718,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.6666667,
          "startTime": 5.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりに、星見のステージに立てて\n本当に、嬉しい",
      "startTime": 10.9885609587,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8778.105708,
          "startTime": 19.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
