    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせ\nこれ、どうぞ",
      "startTime": 71.8319563707,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3366.6653951,
          "startTime": 75.1986217658
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "これは……男物の、浴衣？",
      "startTime": 74.1986206847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "そう……『みんなで浴衣で』お祭りを回る、から\n{user}さんにも、着てほしい",
      "startTime": 84.9194156486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.5860810437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "最初は……ただ、お店で目にとまって……\n似合いそうだ……って思って",
      "startTime": 91.6194156486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.1860810437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もらってほしい、です",
      "startTime": 94.1860810437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。ありがとう、雫\nでも、こんないいもの……もらってもいいのかな",
      "startTime": 101.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.0848802089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで……これは、推し活と一緒だから\n……私、着替えてくるね",
      "startTime": 111.0848802089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺も着替えてくるよ\n後で、みんなと合流しよう",
      "startTime": 114.8182133516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.989277029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ……浴衣……！\n緊張、してきた……へ、変でも、笑わないで",
      "startTime": 120.4681029519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 125.489277029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの浴衣も\n楽しみにしてる……！",
      "startTime": 127.3559449673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――お祭りを回り始めて一時間後",
      "startTime": 129.889277029,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1966.6687012000068,
          "startTime": 131.8559457302
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.7559449673
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.7559449673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ花火の時間だ\n人が多いからはぐれないようにな",
      "startTime": 135.0666676839,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fireworks-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3906.948677700001,
          "startTime": 138.9736163616
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "花火、きれい……",
      "startTime": 143.5402637005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。花火を見ると夏だなーって感じるよ",
      "startTime": 146.7402535279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "雫はどうだ？　夏といえば――\n雫……？　花火、見なくていいのか？",
      "startTime": 156.3666534424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、こそ……\nその、花火……見ない、の？",
      "startTime": 163.3309616884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに雫に見つめられてたら気になるだろう？",
      "startTime": 168.1309736411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。まだ、言ってなかったけど――\n浴衣、よく似合ってるよ",
      "startTime": 175.0999867757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
